Correction was made for spelling error of Independent in Kedah. There may be discrepancies for the age of candidates as there is no official data released for the attribute.There are many missing data points for age attribute for candidates. If year/date of birth is found, age of candidate shown here is the age of the candidate at the end of 31/12/2018 (with an error range of +/-1 year).There were internal clashes within Gabungan Bersatu Sabah (GSABAH) which affected PHRS, PPRS and STAR. Due to clashes between Berjasa, PAP with PAS, Berjasa and PAP are parked under Other Party columns. TindakMalaysia Network Services PLT is not responsible for any errors or ommissions arising from the original data or its derivatives.
